<h2>Books by Rudy Rucker</h2>
<p ><a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/books/rucker_reviews.htm">Reviews</a> *** <a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/books/foregigneditions.htm"> </a><a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/blog/rudy-rucker-ebooks/">eBooks</a> *** <a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/blog/rudy-rucker-free-books/">Free Books</a> *** <a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/writing">On Writing</a> <br>
<a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/books/foreigneditions.htm">Foreign Editions </a> *** <a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/books/agents.htm">Agents</a><a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/writing"></a> *** <a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/blog">Rudy's Blog</a></p>
<p ><em>36 books from newest to oldest:  25 novels, 5 popluar science books, 1  textbook, 1 book of essays, 1 book of stories,  1 memoir, 1 book of journals, and 1 book of paintings. Also listed are   volumes of writing notes, anthologies, omnibus editions, books edited, audio &amp; video, and  software. Last updated July 19, 2023.</em></p>
