<h2>Editing Projects</h2>
<p><strong><em>Be Not Content</em></strong>, by William J. Craddock. Novel of the psychedelic revolution, originally published 1970. Republished by Transreal Books, with an intro by Rudy. <a href="https://www.rudyrucker.com/blog/2012/05/13/william-craddocks-be-not-content-now-out-as-ebook/">Blog post about the book</a>.</p>
<p><strong><i>MONDO 2000: A User's Guide to the New Edge</i></strong>, 
  edited with Queen Mu and R.U. Sirius. HaperCollins, 1992. (Out of 
  print.) </p>
<p><strong><i>Semiotex(e) SF</i></strong>, edited with Peter Lamborn 
  Wilson and Robert Anton Wilson. Autonomedia 1989. (In print (?) 
  Contact Autonomedia, 55 S. 11th St., Brooklyn, NY 11211-0568.) </p>
<p><strong><i>Mathenauts: Tales of Mathematical Wonder</i></strong>. 
  Arbor House, 1987. (Out of print.) </p>
<p><strong><i>Speculations on the Fourth Dimension: Selected Writings 
  of Charles Howard Hinton</i></strong>. Dover, 1983..  </p>
